No, I'm not accusing anybody who are participating in the discussion of actually being this way, so no need to get all indignant with the denials. Whether you are or not only you know the truth of it.<br>
<br>
NBG's a workable system and ideally it benefits those who are most in need, and it can and does work well each and every day. No doubt people abuse it from time to time, and the paranoia of everybody else on the server's out to get you is not entirely baseless, athought it is greatly exaggerated. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#4D4D4D><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/bthetribunaldotorg.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lonagan>lonagan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>l33t board camper</span><br>  Posts: 104<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(11/25/02 11:45:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2260.topic&index=98>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1>   <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr> when in fact you are attempting to acquire loot that is in no way, shape, or form caster loot. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
